\c 24
\s Simudzai misoro yenyu, masuo!
\d Pisarema raDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Nyika ndeyaJehovha, nokuzara kwayo; Nyika yose navageremo.
\v 2 Nokuti wakaiteya pamusoro pamakungwa, Nokuisimbisa pamusoro penzizi.
\v 3 Ndiani angakwira mugomo raJehovha? Ndiani ungamira panzvimbo yake tsvene?
\v 4 Uyo anamaoko akachena, nomwoyo wakanaka kwazvo; Asingasimudziri mwoyo wake kune zvisina maturo, Neasina kupika nhema.
\v 5 Iye achapiwa mukomborero naJehovha, Nokururamiswa naMwari muponesi wake.
\v 6 Urwu ndirwo rudzi rwavanomutsvaka, Vanotsvaka chiso chenyu, imi Mwari waJakobho. Simudzai misoro yenyu, imi masuo; Musimudzwe imi, magonhi akare-kare; Kuti Mambo wokubwinya apinde.
\v 8 Ndianiko iye Mambo wokubwinya? Ndiye Jehovha ane simba noumhare, Iye Jehovha anoumhare pakurwa.
\v 9 Simudzai misoro yenyu, imi masuo; Muisimudze, imi magonhi akare-kare;
\s Kuti Mambo wokubwinya apinde.
\p
\v 10 Ndianiko uyu Mambo wokubwinya? Jehovha wehondo,
\s Ndiye Mambo wokubwinya.
